==Japanese==
学生 (がくせい, ''gakusei'')

===Noun===
#[[student]] (in school)

Derivations:
*[[小学生]] (しょうがくせい, ''shōgakusei'') - primary (elementary, grade) school student
*[[中学生]] (ちゅうがくせい, ''chūgakusei'') - middle (junior high) school student
*[[高等学校学生]] (こうとうがっこうがくせい, ''kōtōgakkō gakusei'') - high school student; more commonly [[高校生]] (こうこうせい, ''kōkōsei'')
*[[大学生]] (だいがくせい, ''daigakusei'') - college student

See also: [[生徒]] (せいと, ''seito''), [[弟子]] (でし, ''deshi'')
